00:02:52.390 --> 00:02:53.080
Yeah!

00:02:53.390 --> 00:02:56.910
Think about it. With the year we've had, 
what with Teio being injured after the Derby,

00:02:56.910 --> 00:02:58.900
and then what happened to 
McQueen in the Fall Tennoushou,

00:02:58.900 --> 00:03:01.070
Japan Cup, and Arima Kinen...

00:03:01.070 --> 00:03:05.260
